<section class="py-24 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[var(--color-heading)] mb-12">What Is This?</h2>

    <div class="text-text-primary leading-relaxed font-sans text-lg space-y-6 text-left">
      <p>
        We're living through a technological acceleration crisis right now. AI evolving faster than wisdom can integrate it. Attention extracted. Meaning slipping away.
      </p>

      <p>
        The StillPoint explores what happens next, and the path we could choose instead. Follow humanity from 2029 to 2099 and beyond, through crisis to renaissance. Not distant sci-fi. A mirror held up to the choices we're making today.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is a living story project written transparently as a human-AI collaboration. Publishing as it's created. Evolving with your feedback. Not hiding the process—modeling what the story teaches: that technology and human wisdom can serve each other when we can be still and see the value in each.
      </p>
    </div>
